Global Automotive Electronic Parking Brake Market Insights
Automotive Electronic Parking Brake Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Automotive Electronic Parking Brake Market Overview
The global automotive electronic parking brake market was valued at USD 4.62 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 8.95 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.4% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by advancements in automotive technology, the increasing adoption of electric vehicles, and rising demand for advanced driver assistance systems (ADAS). The market is also benefiting from consumer preferences for enhanced safety and convenience features in vehicles. Moreover, stringent government regulations regarding vehicle safety are further driving the adoption of electronic parking brake systems.

